ation</HEAD></NG>'s <NG>legislative <HEAD>program</HEAD></NG>.   <NG><HEAD>Luce Balderas</HEAD></NG>, <NG>a <HEAD>member</HEAD></NG> <PG>of</PG> <NG>the <HEAD>Circle</HEAD></NG> <PG>of</PG> <NG><HEAD>Justice</HEAD></NG> and <NG>a <HEAD>mother</HEAD></NG> <PG>of</PG> <NG><CARDINAL>five</CARDINAL> <HEAD>children</HEAD></NG>, <VG>talked</VG> <PG>to</PG> <NG>the school <HEAD>board</HEAD></NG> <PG>on</PG> <NG><HEAD>behalf</HEAD></NG> <PG>of</PG> <NG>the <HEAD>group</HEAD></NG>.   <NG><HEAD>Speaking</HEAD></NG> <PG>in</PG> <NG>Spanish</NG> <NG>she</NG> <VG>told</VG> <NG>the board <HEAD>members</HEAD></NG> that <NG><HEAD>children</HEAD></NG> <VG>are making</VG> <NG>themselves ill <HEAD>thinking</HEAD></NG> <PG>about</PG> <NG>the WASL <HEAD>test</HEAD></NG> and what <NG>it</NG> <VG>could mean</VG> <PG>for</PG> <NG>them</NG> <PG>if</PG> <NG>they</NG> <VG>don't pass</VG>.   "<NG>There</NG> <VG>are</VG> <NG>other <HEAD>ways</HEAD></NG> <PG>of</PG> <NG><HEAD>testing</HEAD></NG> <VG-INF>to see</VG-INF> <PG>if</PG> <NG><HEAD>children</HEAD></NG> <VG>are learning</VG>, <NG>such</NG> <PG>as</PG> <NG>the <HEAD>Measures</HEAD></NG> <PG>of</PG> <NG><HEAD>Academic Progress</HEAD></NG>, which <VG>gives</VG> <NG>us</NG>, <PG>as</PG> <NG><HEAD>parents</HEAD></NG>, <NG>immediate <HEAD>feedback</HEAD></NG> <PG>on</PG> how <NG>our <HEAD>children</HEAD></NG> <VG>are doing</VG> <PG>in</PG> <NG><HEAD>school</HEAD></NG>," <NG><HEAD>Balderas</HEAD></NG> <VG>said</VG>. "<NG>This <HEAD>kind</HEAD></NG> <PG>of</PG> <NG><HEAD>testing</HEAD></NG> <VG>makes</VG> <NG>more <HEAD>sense</HEAD></NG> <PG>to</PG> <NG>us</NG> and <VG>will help</VG> <NG>all in <HEAD>education</HEAD></NG> <VG>provide</VG> <PG>for</PG> <NG>the <HEAD>gaps</HEAD></NG> <PG>in</PG> <NG><HEAD>student</HEAD></NG> <VG-VBG>learning</VG-VBG> <PG>in</PG> <NG>a more timely <HEAD>manner</HEAD></NG> <PG>than</PG> <NG>the <HEAD>WASL</HEAD></NG>."   <NG>She</NG> <VG>told</VG> <NG>the <HEAD>board</HEAD></NG> that <NG>this</NG> <VG>is</VG> <NG>th